'''黎明蟹科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Matutidae}}）是[[短尾下目|短尾下目]]（[[螃蟹|螃蟹]]）[[饅頭蟹總科|饅頭蟹總科]]的一個科<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal = [[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year = 2009 |volume = Suppl. 21 |pages = 1–109 |title = A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author = Sammy De Grave, N. Dean Pentcheff, Shane T. Ahyong ''et al.'' |url = http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |language = en |access-date = 2014-05-26 |archive-date = 2011-06-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref>，當地人稱之為「''moon crabs''」<ref name="SG">{{cite web |url=http://www.wildsingapore.com/wildfacts/crustacea/crab/matutidae/matutidae.htm |title=Moon crabs, Family Matutidae |language=en |date=2008-10 |publisher=[[Wild_Singapore|Wild Singapore]] |author=Ria Tan |access-date=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2014-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527214513/http://www.wildsingapore.com/wildfacts/crustacea/crab/matutidae/matutidae.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
與另一種會游泳的物種「[[梭子蟹科|梭子蟹科]]」不同的是：梭子蟹科只有最後一對足扁平化成泳肢，但黎明蟹科物種卻是全部五對足皆特化成為泳肢<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wetland.org.tw/trip/class/crab/crabmain.htm |title=台南地區常見的螃蟹 |author=螃蟹先生 |date=2000-04-30 |accessdate=2014-05-25 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203635/http://www.wetland.org.tw/trip/class/crab/crabmain.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以輔助游泳或挖掘。本科物種均為[[侵略_(社會科學)|富侵略性]]的[[獵食者|獵食者]]<ref name="AFD">{{cite web |title=Family MATUTIDAE De Haan, 1835 |work=[[Australian_Faunal_Directory|Australian Faunal Directory]] |publisher=Department of the Environment, Water, Heritage and the Arts |date=2009-10-09 |url=http://www.environment.gov.au/biodiversity/abrs/online-resources/fauna/afd/taxa/MATUTIDAE |access-date=2010-01-17 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110401223427/http://www.environment.gov.au/biodiversity/abrs/online-resources/fauna/afd/taxa/MATUTIDAE |archive-date=2011-04-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==分類==
傳統來說，本科過往只有[[黎明蟹屬|黎明蟹屬]]（''Matuta''）一個屬，獨自成為[[饅頭蟹總科|饅頭蟹科]]的一個亞科<ref name="AFD"/>。現時，本分類被升格為科，包括有六個屬，當中有四個現存屬和兩個化石屬<ref name="Grave"/>。儘管本分類依然留在升格成為總科的饅頭蟹總科之內，現時我們仍未了解到底黎明蟹科及新的饅頭蟹科兩個分類的物種之間是否有緊密的關係<ref name="Ng">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2008 |volume=17 |pages=1–286 |title=Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant Brachyuran crabs of the world |author=Peter K. L. Ng, Danièle Guinot & Peter J. F. Davie |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |language=en |access-date=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606061453/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

