==化石紀錄==
''[[Szaboa|Szaboa]]''是現時已知唯一來自[[匈牙利|匈牙利]][[中新世|中新世]]中期[[化石|化石]]沉積層的物種<ref name="Karasawa">{{cite journal |journal=[[Bulletin_of_the_Mizunami_Fossil_Museum|Bulletin of the Mizunami Fossil Museum]] |volume=29 |year=2002 |pages=93–94 |title=First record of a Miocene matutid crab (Crustacea: Decapoda: Brachyura) from Japan |author=Hiroaki Karasawa |url=http://www.city.mizunami.gifu.jp/sightseeing/mizunami/cultural_property/institution/Bull29/BMFM29-093-094(76kB).pdf?PHPSESSID=ab344723232868688e7e59c049311f4a |access-date=2014-05-26 |archive-date=2005-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051220230845/http://www.city.mizunami.gifu.jp/sightseeing/mizunami/cultural_property/institution/Bull29/BMFM29-093-094(76kB).pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，''[[Eomatuta|Eomatuta]]''同樣來自中新世中期的地層，於2009年在[[意大利|意大利]]發現<ref>{{cite journal |author=A. de Angeli & L. Marchiori |year=2009 |title=''Eomatuta granosa'' n. gen., n. sp. (Decapoda, Brachyura, Matutidae), nuovo crostaceo dell'Eocene dei Monti Berici (Vicenza, Italia settentrionale) |journal=Lavori Società Veneziana di Scienze Naturali |volume=34 |pages=105–110 |url=http://www.svsn.it/joomla/volume-34/de-angeli-a.-marchiori-l.-2009.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722053948/http://www.svsn.it/joomla/volume-34/de-angeli-a.-marchiori-l.-2009.html |archivedate=2011-07-22 |access-date=2014-05-26 }}</ref>。[[月神蟹屬|月神蟹屬]]的化石亦有在[[日本|日本]]的中新世地層發現<ref name="Karasawa"/>，但月神蟹屬仍然有現存物種。

